_header: Whilom there was a noble king
_description: Parthenope of Blois (Version B) — in quatrains (abab)

TokyoTak32.First Lines:
[w]hilum ther was a noble kyngeThat was dowghtty holden in
                    dede…
TokyoTak32.Last Lines:
…Theer wiht they casten vp a lowe cryeThee folk they ioynede
                    for heyghe they helde…
